==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Alarmed
<hw>A*larmed"</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Aroused to
vigilance; excited by fear of approaching danger; agitated; disturbed;
<as>as, an <ex>alarmed</ex> neighborhood; an <ex>alarmed</ex>
modesty.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The white pavilions rose and fell⟦br⟧
On the <qex>alarmed</qex> air.</q> <rj><qau>Longfellow.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Alarmedly</ent>⟦br⟧
